WYSIWYM.ontology
Class GeographyOntologyReader

java.lang.Object
  WYSIWYM.ontology.OntologyReader
      WYSIWYM.ontology.GeographyOntologyReader

public class GeographyOntologyReader
extends OntologyReader

This class extends the default ontology reader simply to read a different ontology, i.e. the geography ontology. For the rest it does the same things as OntologyReader.

Version:
1.5 21-08-2008
Author:
Feikje Hielkema
